{"tid":1731470,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［自保建議］手足如果被困睇下可唔可以拍一段身體狀況嘅片","createTime":"2019-11-17T17:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T05:22:45.000Z","uid":134942,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2853c57f20c6320ad3438fddaa78c76eebe0ca","tid":1731470,"uid":134942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:30:40.000Z","msg":"由於唔少救護人員同埋記者都比狗逮捕同禁錮<br />\n手足最壞嘅情況可能唔只被捕,更有可能被折磨甚至被自殺<br />\n想睇下手足可唔可以參考一下黃明志嘅做法<br />\n喺最壞嘅情況發生之前影低自己身體同埋精神狀況<br />\n上公海又好,比信得過嘅人又好<br />\n未必可以做到即時自保,但至少有個根據留低<br />\n唔知道咁樣幫唔幫到手<br />\n如果手足覺得咁樣會留低證據嘅咁幫手拉一拉<a href=\"https://youtu.be/V4aQsPt1dmg?t=94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FV4aQsPt1dmg%3Ft%3D94&d=RPOps9CZsjru%2Bb3lYBIKGi2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=04fc8dd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/V4aQsPt1dmg?t=94</a>"},{"pid":"bab5ca6647989ada10ed1d8cb77176ddd919b657","tid":1731470,"uid":38037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1586a7519a322ea6fb8fbe543afe908c495e4e8b","tid":1731470,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:33:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a5217fd76d057fbe0039370bac2d0d537259d17","tid":1731470,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:33:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b969c6e6b1d09c9ead568770e20342c370d31db1","tid":1731470,"uid":25707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5772eb8d57051f2a2537143a5f9e50e4ac651d","tid":1731470,"uid":237495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:34:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dceb1aef708874c225cf0c529035b6913678030e","tid":1731470,"uid":141097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 